## Elastic Beanstalk

AWS Elastic Beanstalk is a service that makes it easy to deploy cloud  
applications without worrying about the underlying infrastructure. You simply  
upload your code and Elastic Beanstalk handles everything needed to get it  
running, like setting up servers and managing scaling.

Deploying my custom image with Elastic Beanstalk took me about 10 minutes in  
total, including launching the environment.

