## Deploying App Updates

To learn how to deploy app updates with Elastic Beanstalk, I updated my app by  
adding a new line of code alongside an image. I verified those changes by  
opening the `index.html` file in my browser.

My app updates didn't show up immediately because I had to wait for the  
environment to change from grey to green. To deploy changes, I used the  
**Upload and deploy** button.

